snippet: Louis Oosthuizen and Adam Scott each had a seven-under 65 to share a one-shot lead after the opening round of the HSBC Champions in Shenzhen, China.
abstract: Louis Oosthuizen and Adam Scott share first-round lead at HSBC Champions golf tournament in Shenzhen, China.
lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen and Adam Scott each had a seven-under 65 to share a one-shot lead after the opening round of the HSBC Champions in Shenzhen, China.
